        </li>
        <li>Roaming Hunger employees are able to edit the title of existing todos.</li>
        <li>Roaming Hunger employees are able to destroy each todo.</li>
        <li>Roaming Hunger employees are able to check and uncheck checkboxes.</li>
        <li>
          Checking and unchecking the boxes will be able to modify the todo where it would strikethrough the text and
          change the data of done to true and vice versa.
        </li>
        <li>Error are displayed when title is not present during creation and edit.</li>
        <li>Added fontawesome icons for Edit and Destroy buttons.</li>
